<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      metal:use-macro="context/main_template/macros/master"
      i18n:domain="uu.chart">
<head>
<metal:block fill-slot="javascript_head_slot">
<script>

(function ($) {
    "use strict";

    var toggled = false;
    
    function toggleCheckboxes(context) {
        if (toggled) {
            $(context).attr('checked', false);
            toggled = false;
        } else {
            $(context).attr('checked', 'CHECKED');
            toggled = true;
        }
    }

    $(document).ready(function () {
        var select_all = $('#select-all-chart-checkboxes'),
            target = $('.apply-styles .chartlist input');
        select_all.click(function () {
            toggleCheckboxes(target);
        });
    });

}(jQuery));

</script>
</metal:block>
<metal:block fill-slot="style_slot">
<style>

div.style-tools>div {
    border:1px solid #999;
    margin:0.5em;
    padding:0.3em;
}

div.style-tools {
}

.stylebook-creation, .existing-control {
    width:46%;
    float:left;
    border-radius:0.4em;
    padding:0.5em;
}

.stylebook-creation {
    background-color:#f0fff9;
}

.add-button {
    margin:0.6em 0.2em;
    padding:0.4em 0.1em;
    background-color:#dfd;
}

.add-button a {
    text-decoration:none;
    border-bottom:none !important;
    display:block;
    width:100%;
}

.add-button a:before {
    content:"\2009\002b\2009";
}

.existing-control {
    background-color:#ddd;
}

.apply-styles {
    clear:both;
    background-color:#fffff0;
}

.apply-styles ul {
    width:40%;
    float:left;
    padding:0.5em;
}

#select-all-chart-checkboxes {
}

.selcharts {
    clear:both;
    border-bottom:none !important;
    padding:0.5em;
    text-align:right;
}

.style-tools input.apply-button, .add-button {
    font-size:100%;
    font-weight:bold;
    height:2em;
    border-radius:0.3em;
    border:1px solid #999;
    margin-right:0.5em;
}

.style-tools .notes {
    margin:0.5em;
    padding:0.5em;
    font-size:90%;
    color:#888;
}

p.stylebook-desc {
    font-size:85%;
    color:#aaa;
}

.subtle {
    font-size:80%;
    color:#9bb;
    font-style:italic;
    border:1px solid #ddd;
}

.subtle:before {
    width:2em;
    background-color:#ddd;
    content:"\2009\2009\2009\2009\2009\2009";
    margin-right:0.5em;
}

</style>
</metal:block>
</head>
<body>
<div metal:fill-slot="main">

<div class="navmisc">
  <a href="../view">Back to report â†µ</a>
</div>

 <div class="stylebook-listing">
  <h2>Themes for: <em tal:content="context/Title">REPORT TITLE</em></h2>
  <tal:block condition="view/stylebooks">
    <ul>
        <li tal:repeat="stylebook view/stylebooks">
            <a href=""
               target="_blank"
               tal:attributes="href string:${stylebook/absolute_url}/edit"
               tal:content="stylebook/Title"
               >STYLEBOOK TITLE</a>
            <p tal:condition="python: stylebook.Description().strip()"
               tal:content="stylebook/Description"
               class="stylebook-desc"
               >Description</p>
        </li>
    </ul>
    <p class="subtle">Links to edit themes will open in a new window or tab.</p>
  </tal:block>
  <p tal:condition="python: not view.stylebooks()">There are no themes directly within in your report.  There may be themes within project measure groups, but these are not listed here.</p>
 </div>
 <div class="style-tools">
  <h3>Theme tools</h3>
  <div class="stylebook-creation">
      <div class="add-button"><a class="create-button" href="++add++uu.chart.stylebook">Create new theme</a></div>
      <div class="add-button" tal:condition="view/show_paste"><a class="create-button" href="object_paste">Click here to paste copied theme.</a></div>
  </div>
  <div class="existing-control" tal:condition="view/charts">
   <form method="post">
    <p>Create a new theme based on an existing chart:</p>
    <select name="existing-charts">
      <option tal:repeat="chart view/charts"
              tal:attributes="value chart/getId"
              tal:content="chart/Title"
              />
    </select>
    <input type="submit" class="apply-button" value="Create theme based on this chart" name="existing-mimic" />
   </form>
  </div>
  <div class="apply-styles" tal:condition="view/stylebooks">
    <h3>Apply a theme to charts</h3>
    <form method="post">
      <ul class="booklist">
        <li tal:repeat="stylebook view/stylebooks">
            <input type="radio"
                   name="selected-stylebook"
                   tal:attributes="value stylebook/getId;
                                   id string:apply-stylebook-${stylebook/getId}"
                   />
            <label tal:attributes="for string:apply-stylebook-${stylebook/getId}"
                   tal:content="stylebook/Title">LABEL</label>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <ul class="chartlist">
        <li tal:repeat="chart view/charts">
            <input type="checkbox"
                   name="selected-charts:list"
                   tal:attributes="value chart/getId;
                                   id string:selected-charts-${chart/getId}"
                   />
            <label tal:attributes="for string:selected-charts-${chart/getId}"
                   tal:content="chart/Title">LABEL</label>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="selcharts"><a href="javascript:void(0)" id="select-all-chart-checkboxes">Select all charts</a></div>
     <br />
     <input class="apply-button" type="submit" value=" &#x2194; Bind selected themes to selected charts" name="bind-stylebook" />
     <input class="apply-button" type="submit" value=" &#xd7;1 Apply selected themes just once" name="apply-stylebook" />

     <div class="notes">
      <h5>Notes</h5>
      <p><em>* If you bind selected themes, updates to a theme will update the associated charts.  If you apply only once, subsequent updates will not be applied automatically.</em></p>
      <p>Only one theme can be applied to any chart, though you may change which is applied at any time.</p>
     </div>
    </form>
  </div>

 </div>

  <div>
    <h5>To create a new theme, you can:</h5>
    <ol>
      <li><a href="++add++uu.chart.stylebook">Create an original theme.</a></li>
      <li>
            Paste a theme from another report:
            <em tal:condition="not:view/show_paste">
                no themes are currently in clipboard or
                the clipboard contains non-theme items.
            </em>
            <a href="object_paste" tal:condition="view/show_paste">Click here to paste.</a>
      </li>
      <li>Create a theme based on an existing chart (below).</li>
    </ol>
    <p class="subtle">To remove a theme, visit the <a href="folder_contents">folder contents</a> tab of the report.</p>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
